A quiet bike is a happy bike. Stay ninja with the @rideshimano XTR group. Now available at @competitivecyclist 🥷🏼
 
The XTR M9100 series brings a new level of drivetrain silence thanks to decreased tension in the low gear position and an added bumper on the pulley cage. Larger 13T pulleys increase efficiency and chain management while compatibility with SHIMANO's new 12-speed cassettes boosts range.

Farewell @evilbicycles , what a ride it has been ✌🏻⠀
⠀ 
After nearly 10 years of riding and 4 years of employment, I will be moving on from the Evil Bikes family. As years come and go, the good times and memories from my time at Evil will stay with me forever. Thank you to everyone at @evilbicycles for the years of good times and unconditional support 🍻 ⠀
⠀ 
As one door closes, a new one opens. I am looking forward to embarking on this new chapter with some exciting news ahead 🤙🏻 ⠀
⠀
#bleedblackdieevil

Stoked to announce that I will be joining the @gtbicycles family as Head of Product 🤝🏼⠀
⠀
GT has a rich history of innovation and iconic products. I am looking forward to joining the already star-studded team going into the next chapter of the @gtbicycles tale 🙌🏻⠀
⠀ 
What better way to start than with the all-new @gtbicycles Sensor. Redesigned from the ground up, the new Sensor is 140mm of trail trail ripping, jump shredding fun 🤙🏻 ⠀
⠀
Let the good times roll! 🍻⠀
⠀
#gtbicycles #goodtimes ⠀
